<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>McLaren P1 Guide</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa, #c3cfe2);
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #333;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #3498db;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    p, ul {
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: disc;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Card Styles */
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    /* Images Section */
    .images {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .images img {
      max-width: 60%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .images img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Video Section */
    .video-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .video-container iframe {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 5px solid #3498db;
    }
	.video-container:hover {
	transform: scale(1.05);
	}

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .images img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .video-container iframe {
        height: 250px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>McLaren P1 Guide</h1>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The McLaren P1 is a groundbreaking hybrid hypercar that combines cutting-edge technology with breathtaking performance. As part of McLaren's Ultimate Series, the P1 is designed to deliver an unparalleled driving experience, blending the power of a twin-turbocharged V8 engine with an electric motor for exceptional performance and efficiency.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Single Image Section -->
    <div class="images">
      <img src="https://f1rstmotors.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ff1rst-motors.s3.me-central-1.amazonaws.com%2Fcars%2F1713884746548-blob&w=3840&q=100" alt="McLaren P1 Image">
    </div>

   
    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Hybrid Powertrain:</strong> Combines a 3.8-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine with an electric motor, producing a combined 903 horsepower.</li>
        <li><strong>Top Speed:</strong> Electronically limited to 217 mph (350 km/h).</li>
        <li><strong>Acceleration:</strong> 0-60 mph in just 2.8 seconds.</li>
        <li><strong>Design:</strong> Aerodynamic and lightweight, with a focus on performance and efficiency.</li>
        <li><strong>Exclusivity:</strong> Limited production run of 375 units, making it a rare and highly sought-after hypercar.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Performance Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Power Output:</strong> 903 horsepower and 664 lb-ft of torque.</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> 7-speed dual-clutch automatic with rear-wheel drive.</li>
        <li><strong>Braking:</strong> Carbon-ceramic brakes with regenerative braking for the hybrid system.</li>
        <li><strong>Weight:</strong> 3,075 lbs (1,395 kg), thanks to extensive use of carbon fiber.</li>
        <li><strong>Electric Range:</strong> Up to 6.8 miles (11 km) on electric power alone.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
 <!-- Video Section -->
    <div class="video-container">
      <h2>Learn More About the McLaren P1</h2>
      <iframe
        width="560"
        height="400"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/t9-cMiEDNyk" <!-- Replace with a relevant McLaren P1 video -->
        title="YouTube video player"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
    <!-- Technology Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Hybrid System:</strong> Combines a gasoline engine with an electric motor for instant torque and improved efficiency.</li>
        <li><strong>Active Aerodynamics:</strong> Features an adjustable rear wing and airbrake for optimal downforce and stability.</li>
        <li><strong>Driving Modes:</strong> Offers multiple driving modes, including E-Mode (electric-only), Hybrid, and Track mode.</li>
        <li><strong>Lightweight Construction:</strong> Uses advanced materials like carbon fiber and titanium to reduce weight and enhance performance.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>